{"tid":1942212,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】美國海軍的羅斯福號航空母艦上有三名官兵中了武漢肺炎","createTime":"2020-03-25T02:44:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T04:38:14.000Z","uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1e9737e324c52ae592327265e94fc74fdea842ab","tid":1942212,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T02:44:18.000Z","msg":"【突發】美國海軍的羅斯福號航空母艦上有三名官兵中了武漢肺炎，有很大可能是之前在越南蜆港訪港的時候染上的，這5000人的海上城市很有可能在未來一段時間繼續有更多人確診，這次也是首次在部署中的艦艇上發現有官兵確診武漢肺炎的個案。目前海軍已經有86名官兵及民間雇員確診了肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n-DDG54<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.usni.org/2020/03/24/3-sailors-on-uss-theodore-roosevelt-have-covid-19-port-calls-canceled-as-navy-investigates-outbreak\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.usni.org%2F2020%2F03%2F24%2F3-sailors-on-uss-theodore-roosevelt-have-covid-19-port-calls-canceled-as-navy-investigates-outbreak&d=D0cCki4bmudO7bhudq%2Byn9OI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=33b7707a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.usni.org/2020/03/24/3-sailors-on-uss-theodore-roosevelt-have-covid-19-port-calls-canceled-as-navy-investigates-outbreak</a>"},{"pid":"c28545af961c2dad13ffb85ab1e098ce4bf31fb8","tid":1942212,"uid":274723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T02:46:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />美軍頂住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60e379fbf0e3b4e87b86f5e7d4a4d63b037cd117","tid":1942212,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T04:01:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b1a6229ffa03c2149ff4b3df648f3805cf80c06","tid":1942212,"uid":248290,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T04:16:21.000Z","msg":"支那狗 知道 硬碰 打唔贏美帝 先出陰招 玩生化武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/w